# Environment Overview

**Subscription:** ${sub:text}

**Subscription ID:** ${sub}

**Region:** ${region}

---

This dashboard shows the operational status of the Azure environment associated with the selected subscription.

All metrics, alerts, and resource information below automatically reflect the selected environment.

azureResourceGraph.query:
Resources
| where subscriptionId == ${sub:singlequote}
| summarize ResourceCount = count()

Resources
| where subscriptionId == ${sub:singlequote}
| summarize Types = dcount(type)

azureLogAnalytics.query:
let startDateTime = $__timeFrom;
let endDateTime = $__timeTo;
let trendBinSize = 5m;
let maxResultCount = 10;

let summaryPerComputer =
Perf
| where TimeGenerated between (startDateTime .. endDateTime)
| where CounterName == "% Processor Time"
| where InstanceName == "_Total"
| extend ComputerId = iff(isempty(_ResourceId), Computer, _ResourceId)
| summarize Average = avg(CounterValue), Max = max(CounterValue) by ComputerId, Computer
| top maxResultCount by Max desc;

let computerList =
summaryPerComputer
| summarize by ComputerId, Computer;

Perf
| where TimeGenerated between (startDateTime .. endDateTime)
| where CounterName == "% Processor Time"
| where InstanceName == "_Total"
| extend ComputerId = iff(isempty(_ResourceId), Computer, _ResourceId)
| where ComputerId in (computerList)
| summarize TrendValue = max(CounterValue)  by Computer, bin(TimeGenerated, trendBinSize)
| order by TrendValue desc

Perf
| where CounterName == "% Committed Bytes In Use"
| summarize AvgAvailableGB = avg(CounterValue) by bin(TimeGenerated, 5m)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

